><span></span></div><div>Agnes Denes who in 1982, planted a two-acre wheatfield on an empty landfill just two blocks from Wall street and close by to the then World Trade Center. Agnes along with two other assistants and a group of volunteers maintained the field for around four months before harvesting it in the summer. in the end the field produced around 1000 pounds of healthy golden wheat.

Planting and harvesting a field of wheat on land then worth $4.5 billion created a powerful paradox. this piece of art symbolized a universal concept; it represented food, energy, commerce, world trade, and economics. referring to humanity’s mismanagement of world hunger, waste and environmental concerns.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/BFtTbud</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[alwaysbrushyourteeth]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cats with jobs</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/pVfS6q5</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XVKbPGx.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/pVfS6q5</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[tampacl]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cold Weather Dump</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/6BbGWiK</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DmcIHsV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Monkey brain is gonna solve problems like monkey.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TDIliH3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Low on dopamine get the pokeamine.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pvTemSS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My mother and sister are both RNs and nursing stories are always entertaining.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ADGrpw2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Reject society. Go feral.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bGXaOaO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>You're "what does this face mean" autism test won't work on me as I have had to memorise every facial expression and emotional response to survive for the last 30 years.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6wiaeHV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I just really related to this panel and had to save it on my phone.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kCxlaGm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>"A well trained team of professional clowns could run this place more efficiently than you." Is a brutal and supreme insult.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/elaAHpS.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Anyone else grow up on a farm? This is hilariously real.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RHQng3J.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I think stupid cat videos speak for themselves.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ygrj6gB.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Spaniel jowls are precious.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XopIkLi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>..... package?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mTZU04M.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SlwHIWb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Do you know how much time and energy it takes to hide the fact that I am at best a semi domesticated goblin?!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/258rP3U.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I love new places and experiences as long as there are no expectations on me.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kRCp91Y.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The word "embrace" is doing a lot of heavy lifting  here.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ROMkRPT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sounds like a panic at the disco song.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qROODf1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Polyamory: because you are too much work for one petson.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3VIFeT6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is the best kind of absurd humor.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RJZH4XA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>markmedownasscaredandhorny.gif</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JNynYNq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Just a bunch of silly little guys.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7UbBNoW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A pygmy goat headbutt-ed me into a large hole our dog dug in the yard when I was a young child.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UtKIMZF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The ... is a powerful force.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/n3yUYQv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Never could keep a tamagotchi alive.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/G14lpPX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I am very good at entertaining drunk people in shuttle busses. This is a very specific and useless talent.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BWACxgU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And I don't want the world to see me cuz I don't think that they'd understand.....</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Un1f4HP.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Hl4aY0N.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Your sarumom jokes.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GeMExsT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Feel free to use dubious widget face to express doubt when necessary.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EkMqE5x.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is Whiskey trying to fit her whole self in my hand.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zosxH03.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>She's seen some shit.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0QQRAoS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Toe beans!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/6BbGWiK</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Jamceratops]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Spectacular staffy</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/xlUM6tt</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6oSs8oE.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/xlUM6tt</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DOcelot]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>ATT: MAGAts</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/VxCzCNr</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7FB7irj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/VxCzCNr</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ZipQuick]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Very distinguished gentleman</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/PORqsI0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7XJ9COC.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/PORqsI0</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[tampacl]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cat Huffing</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Qv7uc61</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6BXFZoK.gif" style="max-width: 90%; 